NAME
    podusage - Reading usage format from POD.

SYNOPSIS
     hello$ podusage [OPTIONS] [FILE]

OPTIONS
    Some extra options text.

    --help -? --usage
        Display the usage message and exit

    --man
        Display man page

DESCRIPTION
    This program will read the given input file(s) and do something useful
    with the contents thereof.

